OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning low cloud and fog will
OL,6,Fquickly disperse to leave a fine and
OL,7,Fsunny day. Feeling very warm or hot in
OL,8,Fthe strong July sunshine, with light
OL,9,Fwinds for all.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA warm and sunny evening.
OL,12,FStaying clear overnight, but the risk
OL,13,Fof some patches of mist and fog
OL,14,Fforming once more. A warm night for
OL,15,Fmost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FEarly fog clearing to leave a
OL,18,Fhot and sunny day across the region.
OL,19,FLight winds and high UV levels
OL,20,Fexpected. A very warm evening and
OL,21,Fnight to come too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
