OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fdry, sunny and very warm throughout.
OL,7,FThe wind picking up a little may just
OL,8,Fallow it to feel not quite as hot for
OL,9,Fmost. Nights remaining warm.
